r: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>I=
n </span><em>The Good Thing About Hard Things, </em><span>I wrote that &#82=
20;Hard startups on the bits side are solving difficult technical challenge=
